author: vmassol
msg: Moved AbstractTestSuite to an internal package. It's not supposed to be manipulated by the end user. Also, even though ServleTestSuite inherit from it there is no public methods in it that is used by end users. Thus I don't think there will be any dependency on it in any user .class file which would later lead to binary incompatibilities... Let me know if you think otherwise :-)

author: vmassol
msg: Moved AbstractCactusTestCase and CactusTestCase to an internal package. They're not supposed to be manipulated by the end user. Also, even though ServletTestCase and such inherit from them there are no public methods in them that are used by end users.
